posting_body: ['*McKinney*', "This stunning community features classic charm, beautiful architectural design, world-class amenities and, also provides the conveniences that you've come to expect from luxury living.", "You'll find a wide range of thoughtful design touches throughout this beautiful property.", 'Each apartment home features open, airy and spacious layouts with premium materials and finishes found throughout.', 'Please call or text Spirit Real Estate Group at', 'show contact info', 'and refer to property code M-SPSA-1 for more information.', 'We are one of the premier locating services in Dallas.', 'Let us help you find your dream apartment!', '<URL>', 'Facebook: Dallas Upscale Apartment Locators', 'Price and availability subject to change without prior notification.', '*McKinney*', 'We service Downtown Dallas, Uptown Dallas, Richardson, Highland Village, Old East Dallas, East Dallas, Frisco, Plano, North Dallas, Carrollton, Mckinney, Allen, Farmers Branch, Lewisville, Grapevine, Las Colinas, and all of the DFW Metroplex.', '**Ask us how to receive a cash rebate**']
